OL,3,CFlights to and from Tenerife's
OL,4,Cairports disrupted as island hit by
OL,5,Crare snow
OL,7,FTenerife has been hit by snow as Storm
OL,8,FTherese brought adverse weather
OL,9,Fconditions to the Canary Islands.
OL,11,FSpain's weather service AEMET has said
OL,12,Fthe bad weather is expected to last
OL,13,Fseveral days and warned of strong
OL,14,Fgusts that could cause localised
OL,15,Fflooding and landslides.
OL,17,FWinds of more than 90 kilometres an
OL,18,Fhour are expected on the highest
OL,19,Fpoints of the Canary Islands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
