OL,3,CFlights to and from Tenerife's
OL,4,Cairports disrupted as island hit by
OL,5,Crare snow
OL,7,FLocal broadcaster RTVE warned of
OL,8,Fpotentially heavy snow and rain at
OL,9,Fhigher altitudes, with heavy downpours
OL,10,Falso forecast for western Andalusia
OL,11,Fand the Strait of Gibraltar.
OL,13,FFlights to and from Tenerife's
OL,14,Fairports have been cancelled or
OL,15,Fredirected, while universities on the
OL,16,Fisland have suspended teaching.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
