OL,3,CFlights to and from Tenerife's
OL,4,Cairports disrupted as island hit by
OL,5,Crare snow
OL,7,FStorm Therese moved to the Canary
OL,8,FIslands on Thursday, and over 100
OL,9,Fincidents have since been reported,
OL,10,Fmostly related to snow and wind, local
OL,11,Fmedia said.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
