OL,3,CFlights to and from Tenerife's
OL,4,Cairports disrupted as island hit by
OL,5,Crare snow
OL,7,FThe Spanish government issued official
OL,8,Falerts for rain, wind and waves across
OL,9,Fthe Canary Islands, and said the
OL,10,Fdifficult conditions would continue
OL,11,Fthrough the weekend.
OL,13,FThe storm is expected to subside on
OL,14,FSunday but rain will continue
OL,15,Fthroughout next week.
OL,17,FStorm Therese was named by the
OL,18,FPortuguese weather office on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
